ect, not the Go backend\n- The migration follows the planned architecture: city-
builder UI components now use the base `src/ui/` component layer (UIPanel, UIBut
ton, UIText, UIList, UIDialog, etc.)\n- No cross-layer violations\n- Proper depe
ndency injection through constructor config\n\nPotential remaining issues:\n1. `
ConfirmationDialog.ts` lines 66-67 still uses `(this as unknown as { config: ...
