g)` but don\'t rebuild the panel, so visual content won\'t update if you pass ne
w building info/resources. This is a pre-existing pattern and acceptable if dial
ogs are recreated each time.\n3. `BuildingDetailPanel.ts` line 146: `isIdle` che
ck uses template literal. This is a bit fragile - if enum values change, the str
ing won\'t match. But this was likely pre-existing behavior.\n4. `UIList.ts` lin
e 93: horizontal layout division - safe because inside forEach on items array.\n
